name: Trippy Introduction
description:
This piece is a token of admiration and a tribute to the one and only Arief Witjaksana aka Witjk. Been admiring him not only for his distinctive art but his kindness as well. He once bought my piece of secondary for 25 XTZ and it's the highest sale I've got so far on HEN so of course I won't forget. Ever.

Hope this piece could resonate you with his humility and modesty. Also, I'm hoping that this piece is just the beginning of our friendship.
